//They interrupt you.// 

I'm Nona.

[["Ah, ehm. Hi."  ->AhEhmHi]]

//They gesture towards the nearest seat, currently taken by a holographic cowgirl. It flickers and vanishes, and you sit down.//

[["What are we playing?" ->WhatAreWe]] 

[[Continue. ->SoACowboy]]

//You'r not sure what to say next and feel your cheeks getting hot. Nona is looking at you silently.//

[["Could I... sit down?"->CouldIJoin]]

[[Move away from the table.->LEAVING]]

//You get up, and immediatly a holographic Cowgirl takes your place. The game begins in silence, and while you've played various forms of Poker and other card games before, you have a hard time following the game. It seems as if it has almost nothing in common with regular poker. Both of them gesture towards the thin air, throw their cards away, smile, roll their eyes, and generally seem to have an itneresting, if silent, conversation.


You'r not sure what exactly is happening, but they seem to be having a good time.//

[[LEAVING]]
